description: Blue-speckled sea glass walls rise from a glazed bamboo floor.  Just above an intricate sea creatures display hangs a mounted sea monster head, and a low skylight-set ceiling completes the picture.  An aqua-hued seaglass display and a salt-crusted sandstone case stand side by side in the middle of the room.
